from allan allan sullivan subject don cherry coach corner summary april here be a summary of don cherry coach corner from april it take place in the first intermission of game of the montreal-quebec series pre-game comment don pregame comment be mostly aim at the goaly the goalie who get back hi all-star form roy or hextall can win the series for hi team eposode summary thi episode take place rinkside don wa hold a hot dog that he buy from the concession stand ron maclean start out by show a cartoon which appear in the toronto sun it feature a picture of don who just saw hi shadow and proclaim will you look at dat eh mean another week of me beauty next don talk about the hot dog he wa hold according to him the hot dog at the quebec stadium be the best food in all the arena in the nhl from there don comment on the quebec-montreal game the game have great flow because referee paul stewart call the best game in the nhl in contrast the calgary-la game wa terrible all stop-and-go over minute of penalty call against calgary by dan marouelli it get so that the ref who call the most penalty get to ref in the final next ron show an old picture of don when he wa play for the rochester american of the ahl don recall some of the win that he have in the quebec arena during the memorial cup and the ahl championship finally don and ron discuss keenan become coach of the ranger the ranger be a talented team who underachieve don feel sorry for temporary coach ron smith who have several key injury to leetch and patrick and goaly who go cold don have some criticism for the ranger team the party over adolf keenan be there the ranger organization will no longer be a club ny should be achamed of themself if they go in the tank with adolf there they be hang from the yardarm by their thumb rating nothing too special in thi episode i give it a out of allan sullivan allan department of computing science university of albertum edmonton albertum canada my opinion be mine and mine alone it be a